{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/surge/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Developer's blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"e845d1e1-1bf5-556d-a311-776c8887ca89","excerpt":"Meaning Surge means a sudden and strong movement or increase. It can describe physical motion (like waves or crowds) or metaphorical rises (like emotions or…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#meaning\">Meaning</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#grammar-and-usage\">Grammar and Usage</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#common-verb-patterns\">Common verb patterns</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#common-phrases\">Common Phrases</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#collocations\">Collocations</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#examples\">Examples</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#synonyms-or-related\">Synonyms or Related</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#antonym\">Antonym</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","html":"<h2 id=\"meaning\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#meaning\" aria-label=\"meaning permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Meaning</h2>\n<p><strong>Surge</strong> means a sudden and strong movement or increase. It can describe physical motion (like waves or crowds) or metaphorical rises (like emotions or prices).</p>\n<p>As a <strong>verb</strong>, it means <em>to rise or move suddenly and powerfully</em>.\nAs a <strong>noun</strong>, it refers to <em>a sudden strong increase or rush</em>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"grammar-and-usage\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#grammar-and-usage\" aria-label=\"grammar and usage permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Grammar and Usage</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Verb (intransitive)</strong>: <em>to move quickly and powerfully forward or upward.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Structure: <em>surge + forward/up/through etc.</em></li>\n<li>Example: <em>The crowd surged forward.</em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Noun</strong>: <em>a sudden strong movement or increase.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Structure: <em>a surge of + noun</em> (e.g., <em>a surge of anger</em>, <em>a surge in prices</em>)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"common-verb-patterns\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#common-verb-patterns\" aria-label=\"common verb patterns permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Common verb patterns</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><em>surge forward / up / into / through</em></li>\n<li><em>a surge in demand / prices / energy</em></li>\n<li><em>a surge of emotion / power / excitement</em></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"common-phrases\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#common-phrases\" aria-label=\"common phrases permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Common Phrases</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>surge in demand</strong> – a sudden increase in how much people want something</li>\n<li><strong>surge of emotion</strong> – a sudden strong feeling</li>\n<li><strong>power surge</strong> – a sudden increase in electrical power</li>\n<li><strong>surge forward</strong> – move suddenly ahead</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"collocations\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#collocations\" aria-label=\"collocations permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Collocations</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>verb + surge</strong>: <em>prices surge, emotions surge, waves surge</em></li>\n<li><strong>noun + surge</strong>: <em>price surge, energy surge, crowd surge</em></li>\n<li><strong>adjective + surge</strong>: <em>sudden surge, massive surge, emotional surge</em></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"examples\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-label=\"examples permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>The crowd <strong>surged forward</strong> when the doors opened.</li>\n<li>There was a <strong>surge in demand</strong> for electric vehicles.</li>\n<li>A <strong>surge of anger</strong> rushed through him when he heard the news.</li>\n<li>Electricity bills rose after a <strong>power surge</strong> damaged the system.</li>\n<li>The river <strong>surged over</strong> its banks after heavy rain.</li>\n<li>Hope <strong>surged</strong> in her heart as she saw the results.</li>\n<li>The company’s profits <strong>surged</strong> by 30% last quarter.</li>\n<li>Panic <strong>surged through</strong> the crowd during the blackout.</li>\n<li>There was a <strong>surge of excitement</strong> as the concert began.</li>\n<li>Inflation caused a <strong>surge in prices</strong> across the country.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"synonyms-or-related\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#synonyms-or-related\" aria-label=\"synonyms or related permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Synonyms or Related</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>rise</li>\n<li>increase</li>\n<li>escalate</li>\n<li>soar</li>\n<li>swell</li>\n<li>boost</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"antonym\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#antonym\" aria-label=\"antonym permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Antonym</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>decline</li>\n<li>drop</li>\n<li>decrease</li>\n<li>subside</li>\n<li>fall</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"surge meaning and examples","date":"2025-10-28","description":"English learning materials; surge explanation.","tags":["English","verb","noun"],"featuredImage":{"publicURL":"/static/f2a8a8a044aa6c468bf231c04e667e92/surge.png","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8e8b8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/f2a8a8a044aa6c468bf231c04e667e92/b5658/surge.png","srcSet":"/static/f2a8a8a044aa6c468bf231c04e667e92/acb7c/surge.png 256w,\n/static/f2a8a8a044aa6c468bf231c04e667e92/ccc41/surge.png 512w,\n/static/f2a8a8a044aa6c468bf231c04e667e92/b5658/surge.png 1024w","sizes":"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/f2a8a8a044aa6c468bf231c04e667e92/22bfc/surge.webp 256w,\n/static/f2a8a8a044aa6c468bf231c04e667e92/d689f/surge.webp 512w,\n/static/f2a8a8a044aa6c468bf231c04e667e92/67ded/surge.webp 1024w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw"}]},"width":1024,"height":1024}}}}},"relatedPosts":{"nodes":[]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/siege/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"siege meaning and examples"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/discrepancy/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"discrepancy meaning and examples"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"e845d1e1-1bf5-556d-a311-776c8887ca89","previousPostId":"d94d3da3-25cb-5a33-be1b-448ba87de901","nextPostId":"41ab33de-a816-5793-b6f9-91c36b0b0f3b","relatedPosts":[]}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"],"slicesMap":{}}